data.description: Charming Cape Cod style home in gated Mill Creek Pond. Located in Jenks school district and walking distance to the new Tulsa Classical Academy. Tons of natural light and gorgeous hardwood floors throughout. Multiple living areas located inside and out make this home perfect for entertaining. Large living room with vaulted ceilings and a cozy off-kitchen family room with fireplace. Screened in porch with beautiful brick flooring opens to a private and well manicured backyard. Executive office with private attached bath also functions as a well appointed 4th bedroom on the 1st floor. All of the bedrooms boast large walk-in closets, with additional storage space off the master closet. Neighborhood offers a private stocked pond and walking trails.
